    dc:description "FIGURE 12. Locality records for Leptonetela latapicalis sp. nov., L. biocellata sp. nov. and L. tangi sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623708/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623681>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1A–D. Leptonetela biocellata sp. nov. A. Male holotype, dorsal view; B. Male pedipalpal bulb, ventral view; C. Male pedipalpus, prolateral view; D. As previous, retrolateral view. Scale bars: A, 0.5mm; B, 0.1mm; C–D, 0.2mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623681/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623686>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2A–C. Leptonetela biocellata sp. nov. A. Female habitus, dorsal view; B. As previous, ventral view; C. Female genitalia, dorsal view. Scale bars: A–B, 0.5mm; C, 0.1mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623686/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623690>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4A–D. Leptonetela biocellata sp. nov. A. Female genitalia, dorsal view; B. Female genital area, ventral view; C. Male left pedipalpal bulb, ventral view; D. Male left chelicera, posterior view. Abbreviations: At, atrium; Em, embolus; MA, median apophysis; SD, sperm duct; Sp, spermatheca. Scale bars: A–C, 0.1mm; D, 0.2mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623690/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.2623688>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3A–C. Leptonetela biocellata sp. nov. A. Male left pedipalpus, prolateral view; B. As previous, retrolateral view; C. Carapace of male holotype (showing eyes), dorsal view. Abbreviations: PL, prolateral lobe; TS, tibial spur. Scale bars: A–B, 0.2mm; C, 0.5mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/2623688/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

